{"tid":2504430,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好驚剪頭髮?","createTime":"2021-04-26T01:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T18:17:16.000Z","uid":67454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70affff78c7190ae15a734d3642ae93ca91c550a","tid":2504430,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T01:15:31.000Z","msg":"永遠好似買大細咁，總會嚇你一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明叫唔好剪咁短佢就同我剷青<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剪完變柒頭之後仲問我o唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都剪到咁我仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01729ef806bf1d82d9a3acb10556bb1bab9d5947","tid":2504430,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T01:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6f0dd706122ad733655cbf3d700588a1aba9da","tid":2504430,"uid":352644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"剷青好易生瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知把電剪有無清潔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26703a1298e1065efeef1d5bde97bce2c140ae45","tid":2504430,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:55:10.000Z","msg":"唔剪 留長"},{"pid":"b68f963a0f1fef37e270966655ca5e0f5e93b102","tid":2504430,"uid":41611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:09:36.000Z","msg":"記得有套單元劇<br />\n個男主驚地中海去植髮<br />\n開始時好開心<br />\n點知頭髮生得好快<br />\n有一朝早見到一晚頭髮就長過膊頭<br />\n因為要返工所以想自己剪下修下<br />\n然後竟然每剪一下就有聲怪叫<br />\n<br />\n返工去植髮中文問經理<br />\n太遲啦<br />\n因為果刻佢已經變左人乾<br />\n偽裝成頭髮寄生係佢頭到既外星幼苗已經變態成功<br />\n<br />\n樓主小心"},{"pid":"7523ba38581abc55f7f49e869bab44c33fe246c5","tid":2504430,"uid":349955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b68f963a0f1fef37e270966655ca5e0f5e93b102","tid":2504430,"uid":41611,"like":0,"dislik